overview_summary: The neighboring landowners include one absentee investment-focused LLC and one long-standing local family business. Jensen Acres LLC is an out-of-state entity holding farmland likely for speculative gain, whereas Shamrock Acres LLC is tied to a local farm/kennel family with deep community roots. The former is primarily financially motivated, while the latter may prioritize preserving their rural lifestyle, indicating different stances and influence levels in any development debate.

neighbors.name: Jensen Acres LLC
neighbors.claims: Jensen Acres LLC is an Iowa-formed LLC (established in 2012) with its principal office listed in Omaha, Nebraska [Manta](https://www.manta.com/c/mh1xq5w/jensen-acres-llc). Business records indicate it’s a small operation (approximately $97,000 annual revenue with 2 employees) and no local managers identified, suggesting it functions as an absentee land investment vehicle [Manta](https://www.manta.com/c/mh1xq5w/jensen-acres-llc).
neighbors.influence_justification: Low – Out-of-state ownership with no local presence or employment; minimal direct influence in community affairs beyond owning land

approach_recommendations.engage: Engage the Omaha-based principal directly with a clear financial offer (purchase or lease) emphasizing strong returns; as absentee investors, they are likely driven purely by profit and will respond to economic incentives.

neighbors.name: Shamrock Acres LLC
neighbors.claims: Shamrock Acres LLC appears linked to Shamrock Acres Kennels, a local Dane County dog breeder that has operated since 1957 (incorporated in 1986) [Better Business Bureau](https://www.bbb.org/us/wi/waunakee/profile/dog-breeders/shamrock-acres-kennels-ltd-0694-44012072). The kennel’s owner, Colleen K. McCarthy, serves as its registered agent and is likely behind Shamrock Acres LLC, indicating the property is family-owned with long-standing community ties [Better Business Bureau](https://www.bbb.org/us/wi/waunakee/profile/dog-breeders/shamrock-acres-kennels-ltd-0694-44012072).
neighbors.influence_justification: Medium – Multi-generation local business owners; well-known in the area through their kennel/farm, giving them credibility and local connections (though not a major economic player)

approach_recommendations.engage: Engage Colleen McCarthy and family with a personal, respectful approach; acknowledge their long local stewardship and address any concerns (e.g., noise, safety for animals) with assurances and benefits, to gain their trust or neutralize potential opposition.
